{"id":418012,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/11/微信｜不要为巴黎祈祷/","date":"2015-11-17T05:47:52Z","modified":"2015-11-17T05:47:52Z","title":"微信｜不要为巴黎祈祷","content":"<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl1.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418013\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl1.png\" alt=\"bl1\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl1.png 671w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl1-300x205.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 671px) 100vw, 671px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl2.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418014\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl2.png\" alt=\"bl2\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl2.png 642w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl2-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl2-300x300.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl2-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl2-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 642px) 100vw, 642px\" /></a></p>\n<p>“法国是一个古老的国度，在那里，爱人们可以自由亲吻。”</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl3.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418015\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl3.png\" alt=\"bl3\" width=\"301\" height=\"377\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl3.png 301w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl3-240x300.png 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 301px) 100vw, 301px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl4.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418016\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl4.png\" alt=\"bl4\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl4.png 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl4-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl4-300x300.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl4-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl4-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a></p>\n<p>“巴黎是我们的首都，我们爱音乐，我们爱喝酒，我们爱快乐。”</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl5.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418036\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl5.png\" alt=\"bl5\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl5.png 642w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl5-294x300.png 294w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl5-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl5-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 642px) 100vw, 642px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl6.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418037\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl6.png\" alt=\"bl6\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl6.png 643w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl6-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl6-300x300.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl6-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl6-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 643px) 100vw, 643px\" /></a></p>\n<p>“几个世纪以来，总有崇尚死亡的人试图让我们失去对生活的品味。”</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl71.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418038\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl71.png\" alt=\"bl7\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl71.png 641w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl71-295x300.png 295w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl71-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl71-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 641px) 100vw, 641px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl81.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418039\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl81.png\" alt=\"bl8\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl81.png 642w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl81-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl81-300x300.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl81-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl81-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 642px) 100vw, 642px\" /></a></p>\n<p>“但他们从未达成目标。”</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl91.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418040\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl91.png\" alt=\"bl9\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl91.png 635w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl91-293x300.png 293w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl91-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 635px) 100vw, 635px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl10.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418020\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl10.png\" alt=\"bl10\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl10.png 642w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl10-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl10-300x300.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl10-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl10-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 642px) 100vw, 642px\" /></a></p>\n<p>“最后，胜利总是属于那些有爱心的，热爱生活的人们！”</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl11.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418021\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl11.png\" alt=\"bl11\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl11.png 642w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl11-296x300.png 296w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl11-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl11-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 642px) 100vw, 642px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl12.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418022\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl12.png\" alt=\"bl12\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl12.png 641w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl12-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl12-300x300.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl12-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl12-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 641px) 100vw, 641px\" /></a></p>\n<p>“多么美妙的巴黎座右铭：”</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl13.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418023\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl13.png\" alt=\"bl13\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl13.png 643w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl13-296x300.png 296w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl13-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl13-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 643px) 100vw, 643px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl14.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418024\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl14.png\" alt=\"bl14\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl14.png 644w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl14-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl14-300x300.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl14-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl14-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 644px) 100vw, 644px\" /></a></p>\n<p>“风暴之海面，战舰不沉没。”</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl15.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418025\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl15.png\" alt=\"bl15\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl15.png 508w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl15-234x300.png 234w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 508px) 100vw, 508px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl16.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418026\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl16.png\" alt=\"bl16\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl16.png 642w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl16-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl16-300x300.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl16-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl16-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 642px) 100vw, 642px\" /></a></p>\n<p>“全世界的朋友们，谢谢你们为巴黎祈祷，但是我们不需要更多宗教！我们的信念在音乐、亲吻、生命、香槟和快乐中实现！巴黎，代表着一种生活之道。”</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl17.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418027\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl17.png\" alt=\"bl17\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl17.png 639w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl17-300x201.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 639px) 100vw, 639px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl18.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418028\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl18.png\" alt=\"bl18\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl18.png 643w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl18-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl18-300x300.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl18-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl18-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 643px) 100vw, 643px\" /></a></p>\n<p>“恐怖主义不是一个敌人。恐怖主义是一种操纵方式。如果总是重复：‘我们进入战争’ 而没有勇气指明敌人只能误入歧途。我们的敌人是那些热爱死亡的人，他们在各种形式的外衣包裹之下，他们一直存在。历史善于遗忘，而巴黎在这里站立，并对他们说：去你妈的！”</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl19.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418029\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl19.png\" alt=\"bl19\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl19.png 552w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl19-255x300.png 255w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 552px) 100vw, 552px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl20.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418030\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl20.png\" alt=\"bl20\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl20.png 643w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl20-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl20-300x300.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl20-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl20-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 643px) 100vw, 643px\" /></a></p>\n<p>“今晚死去的人们本来只是出门去以巴黎的方式生活，去喝酒或者去唱歌，他们哪里知道自己会沦为宣布战争的受难者。”</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl21.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418031\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl21.png\" alt=\"bl21\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl21.png 519w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl21-240x300.png 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 519px) 100vw, 519px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl22.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418032\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl22.png\" alt=\"bl22\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl22.png 641w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl22-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl22-300x300.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl22-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl22-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 641px) 100vw, 641px\" /></a></p>\n<p>“其实相对于把我们生死相隔，你们反倒是提醒着我们最为宝贵的：什么是我们的生活之道。”</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl23.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418033\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl23.png\" alt=\"bl23\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl23.png 468w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl23-217x300.png 217w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 468px) 100vw, 468px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl24.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418034\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl24.png\" alt=\"bl24\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl24.png 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl24-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl24-300x300.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl24-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl24-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a></p>\n<p>“迷恋死亡的人们，如果上帝真的存在，他也会憎恨你们。你们已经迷失，从世间直到天庭。”</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl25.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-418035\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl25.png\" alt=\"bl25\" width=\"550\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl25.png 437w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/bl25-300x207.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 437px) 100vw, 437px\" /></a></p>\n<p>由《查理周刊》的法国漫画家Joann Sfar<br />\n于法国当地时间周五晚上创作的漫画，</p>\n<p>以及法国摄影家Willy Ronis所拍摄的40-80年代的法国。</p>\n<p>漫画稿照片提供 by Valentina</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20534],"tags":[29268,29269,11170]}